Emami Expects Volume Growth of 13%-14% This Year, Goenka Says

-- B y   M a l a v i k a   S h a r m a
-- 
2011-10-14T07:09:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/emami-expects-volume-growth-of-13-14-this-year-goenka-says.html
Emami Ltd. (HMN)  expects sales volume to
grow by as much as 14 percent this year, Executive Director
Mohan Goenka said in an interview to Bloomberg-UTV today.  The maker of personal care products expects margins to
remain under pressure due to high input costs, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Malavika Sharma in New Delhi at 
 msharma52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
